hose two programs would be included in the national debt these programs themselves would not be changed but how they are accounted for in the united states federal budget would be the goal of the bill is to improve the accuracy of how some programs are accounted for in the federal budget see alsoedit fannie mae ginnie mae fannie mae and freddie mac a bibliography farmer mac farm credit system sallie mae derivative finance government sponsored enterprise securitization usa funds agency securities mortgage law mortgage loan maxine b baker – president and ceo of the freddie mac foundation –present david kellermann – late cfo of freddie mac canada mortgage and housing corporation referencesedit  a b c d e federal home loan mortgage corporation form k annual report for fiscal year ended december   pdf federal home loan mortgage corporation retrieved  april    tysons corner cdp virginia united states census bureau retrieved on may    contact us freddie mac retrieved on may    a b lockhart iii james b  statement of fhfa director james b lockhart federal housing finance agency archived from the original on  retrieved    a b fact sheet questions and answers on conservatorship pdf federal housing finance agency  archived from the original pdf on september   retrieved    a b goldfarb zachary a david cho binyamin appelbaum  treasury to rescue fannie and freddie regulators seek to keep firms troubles from setting off wave of bank failures washington post pp a retrieved    freddie mac courts investors buffett passes august   archived from the original on  retrieved    christie rebecca september   paulson engineers us takeover of fannie freddie update bloomberg retrieved    adler lynn june   fannie mae freddie mac to delist shares on nyse reuters retrieved    grynbaum michael jolly david september   us takeover of mortgage giants lifts stock markets the new york times the new york times company retrieved    leonnig carol d june   how hud mortgage policy fed the crisis washington p